{
  "stem": "13198.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't hate them, but I just felt I didn't want much to do with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was involved in his making other people-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] you know, protecting them from [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] things that went wrong.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a lawyer, so he always-- if there was any [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] cases to bring to court, he did a lot of all that for nothing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he used to give advice twice a week [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in a school for people who wanted-- couldn't afford to go to a lawyer normally.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And just went, this is the free lawyer, and you could go and ask him anything you wanted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a wonderful man-- a really good person, without sort of showing off or anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And then, one day somebody gave him away to the Nazis, and he was arrested in his office.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "War broke out in 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was about 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never knew who it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think this man was arrested, and the Germans, they probably tortured him to give names of people who did things for the Jews and helped Jews to escape abroad, and-- or hide money, or all things-- hide their possessions.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I mean to say that they-- the Nazis came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came in your house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They liked the clock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put it in their pockets, and off they went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nobody could do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they didn't get a chance to come and just take a bit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they-- when I-- when I-- I was then arrested later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they just came and took the house and everything in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never got anything back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my neighbors were pretty marvelous.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
